          <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary py-3 w-full">Register</a>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="min-h-screen bg-secondary/30">
    <section class="section-spacing">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Everything you need to know about our services and pricing</p>
          </div>

          <div class="elegant-card bg-background p-8 md:p-12">
            <div class="space-y-6" id="faqAccordion">

              <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-trigger"><span>What is included in the setup fee?</span><i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="chevron h-5 w-5"></i></button>
                <div class="faq-content"><p>The setup fee covers initial website design, content migration, domain configuration, SSL certificate installation, and basic SEO optimization. This one-time fee ensures your site launches professionally.</p></div>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-trigger"><span>Can I cancel my subscription at any time?</span><i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="chevron h-5 w-5"></i></button>
                <div class="faq-content"><p>Yes, you can cancel your monthly subscription at any time with no penalties. Your website will remain active until the end of your current billing period.</p></div>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-trigger"><span>Do you provide hosting?</span><i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="chevron h-5 w-5"></i></button>
                <div class="faq-content"><p>Yes, all plans include reliable hosting with 99.9% uptime guarantee, automatic backups, and security monitoring. You don't need to worry about separate hosting arrangements.</p></div>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-trigger"><span>How long does it take to build my website?</span><i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="chevron h-5 w-5"></i></button>
                <div class="faq-content"><p>Most websites are completed within 2-3 weeks from the initial consultation. Complex projects may take longer, and we'll provide a detailed timeline during the quote process.</p></div>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-trigger"><span>Can I update my website content myself?</span><i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="chevron h-5 w-5"></i></button>
                <div class="faq-content"><p>Absolutely. We provide an easy-to-use content management system and training so you can make updates whenever needed. We're also available for support if you need assistance.</p></div>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-trigger"><span>What happens if I need changes after launch?</span><i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="chevron h-5 w-5"></i></button>
                <div class="faq-content"><p>Your monthly subscription includes ongoing maintenance and minor updates. Larger redesigns or new features can be quoted separately based on your needs.</p></div>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-trigger"><span>Do you offer e-commerce functionality?</span><i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="chevron h-5 w-5"></i></button>
                <div class="faq-content"><p>Yes, our Pro and Enterprise plans include full e-commerce capabilities with product catalogs, shopping carts, payment processing, and inventory management.</p></div>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-trigger"><span>Is my website mobile-friendly?</span><i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="chevron h-5 w-5"></i></button>
                <div class="faq-content"><p>All websites we build are fully responsive and optimized for mobile devices, tablets, and desktops. Mobile-friendliness is a standard feature across all plans.</p></div>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-trigger"><span>What kind of support do you provide?</span><i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="chevron h-5 w-5"></i></button>
                <div class="faq-content"><p>We offer email support for all plans, with priority support for Pro and Enterprise customers. Response times are typically within 24 hours on business days.</p></div>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-trigger"><span>Can I upgrade or downgrade my plan?</span><i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="chevron h-5 w-5"></i></button>
                <div class="faq-content"><p>Yes, you can change your plan at any time. Upgrades take effect immediately, while downgrades apply at the start of your next billing cycle.</p></div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->
  <footer class="bg-foreground text-background pt-20 pb-10">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 md:gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="md:col-span-5">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-background text-foreground font-bold text-xl">S</div>
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">SiteSimpl</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-sm">Professional website solutions for businesses of all sizes. Simple, elegant, and effective.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-3 md:col-start-7">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-6 tracking-wide">Navigation</h3>
          <nav class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <a href="index.html" class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-background transition-colors font-medium">Home</a>
            <a href="/plans" class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-background transition-colors font-medium">Plans</a>
            <a href="examples.html" class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-background transition-colors font-medium">Examples</a>
            <a href="faqs.html" class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-background transition-colors font-medium">FAQs</a>
          </nav>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-3">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-6 tracking-wide">Contact</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <a href="mailto:hello@sitesimpl.com" class="flex items-center gap-3 text-muted-foreground hover:text-background transition-colors font-medium"><i data-lucide="mail" class="h-5 w-5"></i> hello@sitesimpl.com</a>
            <a href="tel:+15551234567" class="flex items-center gap-3 text-muted-foreground hover:text-background transition-colors font-medium"><i data-lucide="phone" class="h-5 w-5"></i> (555) 123-4567</a>
            <div class="flex gap-4 mt-4">
              <a href="https://facebook.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-background/10 p-3 rounded-full text-background hover:bg-primary hover:text-primary-foreground transition-all" aria-label="Facebook"><i data-lucide="facebook" class="h-5 w-5"></i></a>
              <a href="https://twitter.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-background/10 p-3 rounded-full text-background hover:bg-primary hover:text-primary-foreground transition-all" aria-label="Twitter"><i data-lucide="twitter" class="h-5 w-5"></i></a>
              <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-background/10 p-3 rounded-full text-background hover:bg-primary hover:text-primary-foreground transition-all" aria-label="LinkedIn"><i data-lucide="linkedin" class="h-5 w-5"></i></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="border-t border-background/10 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
        <p class="text-muted-foreground font-medium">© <span id="year"></span> SiteSimpl. All rights reserved.</p>
        <div class="flex gap-8">
          <a href="/privacy" class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-background transition-colors font-medium">Privacy Policy</a>
          <a href="/terms" class="text-muted-foreground hover:text-background transition-colors font-medium">Terms of Service</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
    const menuBtn = document.getElementById('menuBtn');
    const mobileMenu = document.getElementById('mobileMenu');
    menuBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      mobileMenu.classList.toggle('hidden');
      menuBtn.innerHTML = mobileMenu.classList.contains('hidden') ? '<i data-lucide="menu" class="h-6 w-6"></i>' : '<i data-lucide="x" class="h-6 w-6"></i>';
      lucide.createIcons();
    });

    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-trigger').forEach((btn) => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const item = btn.closest('.faq-item');
        const content = item.querySelector('.faq-content');
        const isOpen = item.classList.contains('open');

        document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item.open').forEach((openItem) => {
          if (openItem !== item) {
            openItem.classList.remove('open');
            openItem.querySelector('.faq-content').style.maxHeight = null;
          }
        });

        if (isOpen) {
          item.classList.remove('open');
          content.style.maxHeight = null;
        } else {
          item.classList.add('open');
          content.style.maxHeight = content.scrollHeight + 'px';
        }
      });
    });

    lucide.createIcons();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
